commitResults.messageTitle: Add the ability to store whatever text user enters and display them back when requested
Add the ability to mark tasks as done. Optionally, add the ability to change the status back to not done.
Add support for tracking three types of tasks - Todo (Task without date/time) - Deadlines (Task done before a specific date/time) - Events (Task that starts and ends at a specific date/time)

ToDos: tasks without any date/time attached to it e.g., visit new theme park Deadlines: tasks that need to be done before a specific date/time e.g., submit report by 11/10/2019 5pm Events: tasks that start at a specific date/time and ends at a specific date/time e.g., (a) team project meeting 2/10/2019 2-4pm (b) orientation week 4/10/2019 to 11/10/2019
